data.description: Come check out this open floorplan, Beautiful, spacious 4bdr/3.5ba split level home w/office and Spacious bonus room w/Half bath. On the main level you'll find your main living area that opens up to the dining space right next to the open concept kitchen area. In the kitchen you'll find newly Updated cabinets, providing plenty of storage space, updated Marble counter tops, Double wall oven, dishwasher, fridge and cooktop. Right off the Kitchen you'll find a huge formal dining room with fireplace. On the main level you'll also find your bonus room/flex room complete w/ half bath. There's also an extra room that can potentially be used as an office or additional living space. Upstairs you'll find your master bedroom with full bath along with 3 additional bedrooms and 2 additional full bathrooms. The huge backyard is completely fenced-in with shed for storage. Come check out this amazing home in a beautiful neighborhood. Schedule your showing today!!
